name: Florida Dealer Consultants
tag_list: dealer-management-system, florida-car-dealer, florida-dealer-consultants, dms, bhph, buy-here-pay-here, dealer-software, dmv-forms
overview:
Florida Dealer Consultants provides Florida-based car dealers with software to help manage their dealership.

The company is made up of software programmers and “consultants”, as they call them, with vast car dealership experience. The programmers work to create innovative dealer software and the consultants help dealers learn how and why to use software in the dealership.

The 2 primary software products offered are: 1) dealer management system called Advanced Car Dealer Manager 2) dealer websites

Florida Dealer Consultants helps simplify the process of selling cars by printing all DMV required forms at the time of sale, managing customers, managing inventory, tracking business and vehicle expenses, helping to successfully operate Buy Here Pay Here (BHPH) financing, and providing the business owner with in-depth business reports that help the owner gauge the direction/success of his or her business.
